        <updateDate>2006-06-27T14:57:23Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Homeland Security Transparency Act of 2006 - Amends the Homeland Security Act of 2002 to direct the Secretary of Homeland Security to: (1) require homeland security grant recipients to submit quarterly reports on each expenditure made using grant funds; and (2) publish and make publicly available on the Department of Homeland Security's (DHS) Internet website a description of each such expenditure.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
